WEBVTT

00:03:57.130 --> 00:04:00.600
which YouTube video you saw,
it’s all there.

00:04:00.600 --> 00:04:04.176
Now if your phone gets hacked
or your account gets hacked,

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:07.760
and trust me it’s not
difficult to do this at all.

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:12.296
To begin with, things you don’t
want disclosed will get disclosed.

00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:16.416
Now what if your bank
account is linked to it?

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:20.176
Or your PAN card or Aadhar card.

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.629
So it can cause a huge loss,
and this is happening.

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.400
A responsible company like Google advises

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:29.400
that you keep deleting your online history
from time to time.

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:33.270
How many of us know,
and even if we do know,